title: Revealing Our Baby's Name!!! + Meet Our Baby Girl! (Birth Vlog Pt. 2)
author: Brittany Xavier
description:
hi guys!! This is a very special video for us! We’re revealing our little girl’s name and the meaning behind it. We’ve had her name picked out since the beginning of my pregnancy and we’re so excited we can share these moments with you! 

This video also includes part 2 of our birth story and everything that happened right after she was born, if you missed part 1 check it out here:
